c: 3
v: 37
t: "Mukama omulabirizi we yamwanukula olwanukula olwa namaddala era naamukuza enkuza ennungi era naamukwasa Zakaria abe omukuza, buli Zakaria lweyayingiranga mu kifo Mariam weyatuulanga olwokusinza ng’amusanga alina ebyokulya. Naagamba nti owange Mariam bino obifuna kuva wa, naamuddamu nti byo biva wa Katonda, mazima Katonda agabirira oyo gwayagadde awatali kubalirira"